description: This is what the market has been waiting for! Spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom duplex with an incredible private backyard! Newly rebuilt private rear deck, exclusive patio and full yard make for an entertainer's dream! Sunny, open concept living room opens into a beautifully updated kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, granite counters, marble backsplash and a dining island! Two bedrooms with double closets plus a full bathroom complete the first floor. Head downstairs to the fully remodeled private oasis, including a full en-suite marble bathroom and spacious room ideal for guests, a home office, or a quiet retreat! Central Air! Laundry! Low HOA + Prime location near the beach, shops, restaurants and more! A rare gem in today’s market! And let's not forget about the HUGE private back yard!
